headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Car Meet Prize Ride: Übermacht Sentinel XS
content:
Placing in the Top 5 in two Pursuit Races this week will earn LS Car Meet members this week’s Prize Ride, the Übermacht Sentinel XS.

To unlock access to the LS Car Meet, head over to see Mimi in Cypress Flats. You can find her location by locating the LS Car Meet icon on the GTA Online Map.
